data.description: The iconic barn in the heart of Short Sands Beach.... awaits your ideas and transformation! This beloved structure built approximately just after the Civil War, soars over 50 feet , with potential ocean views from its top floors. Located just a stones throw to Short Sands Beach & under 1/2 mile to Long Sands Beach. Opportunity  awaits on a renovation to residential or business spaces, with year round town water and sewer right at the front door.  The barn is currently a large timber frame shell awaiting your ideas- current owners have architectural design renderings available upon request.  Do check with the town/ due diligence on options within this zone. Your breath will be taken away by the unique character steeped in history.....oh the possibilities of 7 Justin Circle! Residential Architectural Renderings available so you can see the vision!
